<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">The E Train is not running on Saturday, May 12.</span></strong> Please take the 7 train (you can also take the N train and walk from  Queensboro Plaza, which takes a little longer).</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>walking directions from 7 train:</strong> Walk north on 23rd (walking under the elevated train line) to the green gates on the left side of street. Look for the building with the green "Caffeina" sign. The Secret Theatre is on the left, through the green gates.</p>
